collectors.title: Database
collectors.titleDetails: (8 total Queries, 8 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql:
select *, tc.status
        from tbl_clients as tc, tbl_firm as tf
        where tc.fID = tf.firmID
        and tc.fID = 1

select wpID,wp.added_by,wp.client, wp.auditor, wp.supervisor,wp.audmanager, wp.firm,wp.jobdur,wp.financial_year,wp.end_financial_year,wp.status,wp.remarks,wp.added_on, (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_files_c1 as tc1 where tc1.workpaper = wp.wpID and tc1.clientID = wp.client) as x1, (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_files_c2 as tc2 where tc2.workpaper = wp.wpID and tc2.clientID = wp.client) as x2, (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_files_c3 as tc3 where tc3.workpaper = wp.wpID and tc3.clientID = wp.client) as x3, (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_files_c1 as tc1 where tc1.workpaper = wp.wpID and tc1.clientID = wp.client and updated_on IS NOT NULL) as y1, (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_files_c2 as tc2 where tc2.workpaper = wp.wpID and tc2.clientID = wp.client and updated_on IS NOT NULL) as y2, (select COUNT(*) from tbl_client_files_c3 as tc3 where tc3.workpaper = wp.wpID and tc3.clientID = wp.client and updated_on IS NOT NULL) as y3, (select CONCAT(name,' - ',type) from tbl_users as tu where tu.userID = wp.added_by) as added, (select CONCAT(name,' - ',type) from tbl_users as tu where tu.userID = wp.auditor) as aud, (select CONCAT(name,' - ',type) from tbl_users as tu where tu.userID = wp.supervisor) as sup, (select CONCAT(name,' - ',type) from tbl_users as tu where tu.userID = wp.audmanager) as audm, tc.name as cli, tc.org from tbl_workpaper as wp, tbl_clients as tc where wp.firm = 1 and tc.cID = wp.client and wp.status != 'Approved'
